commentary: Chigumbura to Wahab Riaz, OUT what an effort from Chigumbura. Wahab is walking off. Splendid effort. He makes a run-out of nothing. Wahab's struggle continues as he can only inside-edge a ball back onto his shoe, but he is looking for a single as the ball trickles into the off side. However, Elton is quick on it, and under-arms a throw back onto the stumps as Riaz is sent back - all in one swift motion. Pak are 8 down and EC has his second wicket.
